These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry, vegafina, pall-mall, ritmeester, tiparillo
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, indian, mexican, russian, spanish
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the russian is between the tiparillo-smoker and the american##2
5. the mexican is between the russian and the argentine##2
6. the american is the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the american##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Cigar           | blend | old-henry | tiparillo | ritmeester | pall-mall    | vegafina  |
| Nationality   | spanish | argentine   | mexican       | russian        | american | indian |

