.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, german, italian, thai, turkish
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bluemaster, bongani, chaman, bolivar, siglo
1. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the thai##1
3. the chaman-smoker is between the italian and the argentine##2
4. the german is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
7. the italian is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the dutch is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | dutch | turkish | thai | italian | german | argentine  |
| Cigar           | siglo | bolivar  | oliveros | bluemaster    | chaman  | bongani |

