.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, frog, guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
6 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, snooker, poker, bridge, backgammon
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person playing scrabble##2
7. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | bird | snake      | rabbit | guinea-pig | frog      |
| Game   | monopoly    | backgammon  | scrabble | poker   | bridge       | snooker |

