.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
6 different games are played: canasta, go, backgammon, poker, scrabble, bridge
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, cycling, golf, ice-hockey, soccer
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person playing go is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing scrabble##2
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
8. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Game   | canasta   | poker    | bridge | backgammon | go | scrabble   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton | cycling | soccer | golf  | biathlon |

