.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There 6 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, nectarine, orange, pepper, strawberry
There are 6 different nationalities: russian, argentine, mexican, colombian, chinese, indonesian
1. the russian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the indonesian is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the russian is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
4. the indonesian is on the far right##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the chinese##1
6. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the argentine##1
7. the mexican is the person eating strawberry##1
8. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating orange and the indonesian##2
9. the person eating cauliflower is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Food    | cauliflower | strawberry | pepper  | orange      | nectarine | grapefruit  |
| Nationality   | argentine  | mexican    | colombian | russian | chinese | indonesian |

