3. the oliveros-smoker is between the game-smoker and the havana-smoker##2
4. the havana-smoker is the person driving the van##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
6. the game-smoker is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the tram##2
7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
8. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
