.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
City: miami, london, berlin, nizza, new-york, boston
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, disco, gospel, indie, jazz, trance
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of trance is between the fan of jazz and the fan of blues##2
4. the person traveling to nizza is the fan of gospel##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to new-york##2
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
9. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| City           | nizza | boston | new-york | berlin | london | miami |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | indie   | disco         | blues    | trance     | jazz     |

