.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, gardening, hiking, singing, sudoku
There are 6 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, spanish, egyptian, pakistani, thai
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the egyptian##1
 2. the nigerian is between the person who's hobby is chess and the thai##2
 3. the malaysian is on the far left##1
 4. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the nigerian##1
 6. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the spanish is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | chess   | singing  | filmmaking | hiking | sudoku | gardening     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | nigerian | thai    | pakistani | egyptian | spanish |

