.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, drama, family, horror, satire
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, zinnia, daisy, bellflower, balloon-flower
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person who growstulip is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is the person who growstulip##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
8. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching family movies and the person who growsbegonia##2
9. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | satire | family   | comedy | documentary | horror |
| Flower           | begonia  | daisy   | zinnia | tulip | balloon-flower       | bellflower |

