.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, dancing, chess, skydiving, baking, singing
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, skateboard, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the train##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the train is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the car##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person driving the car and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Hobby         | singing   | baking | chess       | skydiving | woodworking    | dancing |
| Transport   | jet-ski | train  | skateboard | car      | subway | van        |

