.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, snowboarding, swimming, water-polo, rugby, lacrosse
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, family, musical, scientific, sports, time-travel
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 5. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's sport is rugby##2
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Sport           | snowboarding      | water-polo | swimming | baseball   | lacrosse  | rugby |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy  | family             | time-travel | musical | sports       |

