.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
There 6 different types of food: avocado, banana, mango, onion, peas, zucchini
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rowing, tennis, golf, skiing, basketball, biathlon
 1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person eating banana##2
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person eating zucchini and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the person eating zucchini is between the person who's sport is golf and the person eating mango##2
 6. the person eating onion is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person eating onion is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Food   | onion     | avocado | peas   | mango     | zucchini       | banana       |
| Sport    | tennis | skiing   | rowing | basketball | biathlon | golf |

