5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is between the thai and the person who's birthday is in november##2
8. the polish is the person who's birthday is in december##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |   6   |
| Nationality   | polish | australian | nigerian | thai      | turkish | dutch |
| Birthday     | december   | november | october     | august | september  | june   |

