.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, cooking, drawing, rock-climbing, woodworking
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: salsa, r&b, funk, ambient, reggae, rock
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 2. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the fan of ambient is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of r&b is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the fan of funk is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is camping##2
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Hobby         | drawing | camping | collecting | woodworking | rock-climbing | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | reggae | funk      | ambient     | rock       | r&b |

 